<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>Station 395</strong><br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721422" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span><br />
<strong>Image:</strong> <a href="https://pixabay.com/photos/gas-station-night-time-fuel-692045/">Source</a></p>
<p>This article was a photo I found, which I have wanted to write something about for ages, since I found it. I always wanted to do a creepypasta, but never knew what way to take it until Parawatch popped up a few days ago. Unfortunately, that photo is Non-Commercial licensed, so I couldn't use it. A conversation with T Rutherford helped guide the conception of this, and gave me some excellent ideas on how to finish it.</p>
<p>An article for the new and surging <a href="/parawatch-hub">Parawatch</a> Group of Interest.</p>
<p>Thanks to my reviewers: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/t-rutherford" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4620432); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4620432&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721422" alt="T Rutherford" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4620432)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/t-rutherford" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4620432); return false;">T Rutherford</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3656445); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3656445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721422" alt="Ellie3" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3656445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3656445); return false;">Ellie3</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721422" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;">Crashington</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721422" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;">Ihp</a></span> who all helped this article get to it's current form.</p>
<p>View more of my articles <a href="/stormbreath">here.</a></p>
